{"title":"git 添加文件未识别","date":"2018-07-16T23:07:00.000Z","link":"post/157","categories":["Git"],"updated":"2019-06-23T14:31:53.847Z","content":"<p>今天在项目目录下添加了一个.sql类型的文件，但是使用<code>git status</code>缺发现未识别这个文件。<br><strong>解决方法</strong><br>只需在项目文件夹下的<code>.gitignore</code>文件中添加sql类型的文件即可<br><img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/322503200.png\" alt></p>\n","prev":{"title":"php中判断一个时间是今天的时间","link":"post/158"},"next":{"title":"redis安装","link":"post/153"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/157/"}